title: GHA:Mazznoff
author: RonGrundeswaldJr
pages:
#- By the authority of the Grundeswegian throne Mazznoff has been presented with the Golden Heart Award.
This prestigious award is given to individuals who have shown remarkable acts of kindness towards Grundeswald and its peoples. 
#- This certificate is a formal acknowledgement of your deeds and has been personally signed by the Grundeswald royal family noting that you are a commendable individual worthy of praise.
#- 
With this award the recipient is granted the honour of having the post-nominal letters 'GH' applied to their name in all official Grundeswegian documents.
#- 
Recipients are also entitled to be addressed as ‘Sir’ or 'Madam' within Grundeswald proper by all non-distinguished citizens upon request.
#- On behalf of the Grundeswegian nation and its peoples we graciously thank you for your efforts and hope that your generosity extends into the far future.

Signed,
Prince Ronald Grundeswald Jr.
#- 